## âœ… Requirements

- PHP 7.4+ (tested on PHP 8.1)
- MySQL (XAMPP / MAMP / LAMP)
- Web browser

## âš™ï¸ Setup

1. Clone or copy to `/htdocs/lost-found/`
2. Import `users`, `items`, `matches` tables into MySQL
3. Set database name in `includes/db.php`
4. Visit `http://localhost/lost-found/`

